## Why This Is Asked
Tests ability to design robust Saga orchestration with cross-region isolation, outbox reliability, and per-tenant event schemas in an environment using CQRS and event-sourcing.

## Key Concepts
- Saga orchestration across regions with compensations
- Outbox pattern for durable cross-service communication
- Event-sourcing with per-tenant schema versioning
